== 制作 ==
该片的主题是“老师和学生如何‘沟通’”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/m/2011-05-04/13383298771.shtml |title=《跟踪孔令学》：拳头和手掌的辩证关系 |date=2011-05-04|work=新浪 |archive-date=2014-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316052013/http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/m/2011-05-04/13383298771.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>拍摄于[[辽宁省|辽宁省]][[沈阳市|沈阳市]]、[[本溪市|本溪市]]。

该片在内部放映时，据称赢得了[[郎永淳|郎永淳]]、[[路一鸣|路一鸣]]、[[王良|王良]]等[[中国中央电视台|央视]]知名主持人的赞誉。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.qq.com/a/20110415/000050.htm |title=《跟踪孔令学》内部放映 央视名嘴赞不绝口 |date=2011-04-15|work=腾讯网 |archive-date=2014-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316060316/http://ent.qq.com/a/20110415/000050.htm |dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.163.com/11/0418/09/71TMCLVI000300B1.html |title=《跟踪孔令学》获名嘴力捧 4月30日正式公映 |date=2011-04-18 |work=网易 |archive-date=2014-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316063608/http://ent.163.com/11/0418/09/71TMCLVI000300B1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

《[[沈阳晚报|沈阳晚报]]》评价该片是“范伟最差的电影”。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/m/2011-05-09/15373303071.shtml |title=沈阳晚报：《跟踪孔令学》除了表演别的不及格 |date=2011-05-09 |work=新浪|archive-date=2014-03-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316055458/http://ent.sina.com.cn/r/m/2011-05-09/15373303071.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

